description: Presenting 4 Springer Street, a promising 3 bedroom, 1.5 bathroom home ideally situated just .1 miles from the beach in South Boston. This residence offers an exceptional opportunity for both end users and developers. The property features an eat-in kitchen, first-floor laundry and half-bath, and a large back deck, providing an ideal space for customization and expansion. With great ceiling height, this fixer-upper bursts with potential, inviting creativity and vision. Explore the vibrant neighborhood and unlock the endless possibilities of this prime location.
